      • withBagging

        public RandomForestBuilder withBagging(int sampleSize)
        Setting this to a value greater than zero will turn on bagging (see Bootstrap aggregating. Use Integer.MAX_VALUE to set the bag size to be the same as the training set size.
        Parameters:
        sampleSize - The size of each bag, 0 to deactivate bagging (defaults to 0). Will use the smaller of this value and the training set size.
        Returns:
